{"tid":2121512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄建議今屆考生明年放榜日再回校","createTime":"2020-07-23T10:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T12:10:46.000Z","uid":308166,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"27db9cb5c14942dd4ecc8416230798fc6b37482a","tid":2121512,"uid":308166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄表示，今年因應疫情，大部分學校改以電子方式發放文憑試成績通知書，有考生可能覺得，未能在放榜日回校領取成績和拍照是一份遺憾，他對此表示理解，但今次的安排是為了保障大家健康，建議今年的考生在明年放榜日，再次回母校，與師弟、師妹分享經驗和心得，認為是更有意義和難忘的放榜歷程。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄在社交網站表示，從媒體報道得知，肢體傷殘或其他特殊教育需要的學生，以至來自基層家庭的同學，在學習和生活上都遇到較大困難，他們經過努力取得佳績，是社會的驕傲。他又說，文憑試成績不論如何，亦希望考生能繼續努力，按自己的興趣和能力，在多元出路之中，發揮所長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539451-20200723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539451-20200723.htm&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=6043369f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539451-20200723.htm&h=57fe5afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539451-20200723.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f6c1338ddb4db6a7180e05a7f16f67df5024c736","tid":2121512,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6152abcede0c46a799635671b1f34baa81938538","tid":2121512,"uid":321803,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"9up官"},{"pid":"155d642c645236b80058d913f61fa573ae8df736","tid":2121512,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"叫你兩個仔番香港先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2229e83bd580b53c679991aca0948b0b85e09705","tid":2121512,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"佢個兩個仔係邊"},{"pid":"14